Home in Edmonton

4.79 out of 5 average rating, 56 reviews4.79 (56)

Harmony Inn Plus

Welcome to Harmony Inn, a beautiful two-story house located in the heart of Manning, Edmonton. With a park and baseball diamond just a short walk away, this rental gives you lots of opportunities to enjoy the outdoors. Manning Town Centre is minutes away. Boston Pizza, McDonald's Edo Japan, and Cineplex are just a few of the shops this center has to offer. Harmony Inn has 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. A spacious full kitchen is located on the first floor with a living area and dining room.

Condo in Sherwood Park

2 BD 2 BA with A/C & Parking - Sherwood Park

Living here means you’re right in the mix, with easy access to expansive trails, lush parks, family activities, and all the shopping and services you could need. Harmony at the Market is uniquely perched atop The Market at Centre in the Park. Imagine stepping out of your door to Planet Organic, Good Earth Coffee, and a variety of medical services—all under the same roof. Plus, whether you’re commuting to Edmonton’s downtown, Fort Saskatchewan, St. Albert, or Nisku, you are 25 to 28 min away.

Please note...residents upstairs, you may hear footsteps :) 1 SMALL dog only. NO CATS, Very allergic to them :(

Cozy bedroom in a beautiful house

Welcome to our quiet, beautiful and clean house. We offer peaceful space for our guests to have a pleasant stay and get relaxed. Enjoy the beauty of Edmonton - staying next to highway exit and lots of walking trails and green space in Fraser community. Don’t have a car, or need a ride to/from the airport or within city pickup/drop? We can arrange this for reasonable fee if time permits as per our schedule. Feel free to reach out to us for more information.

Rental unit in Edmonton

Lovely 2 bedroom apartment with free parking.

Forget your worries in this spacious and serene space. New LVP floors, paint & stainless steel appliances, including a dishwasher. Elevator in the building, massive balcony with extra storage. Guest(s) can use anything available in the apartment, as you would have the whole apartment to yourself. The master bedroom is what would be used as the other room is not ready. Cute and Cozy Ramada - Free breakfast

Quaint hotel, located just off Baseline Rd in Sherwood Park, with easy access to Yellowhead Trail. We offer in suite amenities, an onsite fitness center, business center, 24/7 customer service and also a FREE breakfast! There are many restaurants close by, including a Boston Pizza directly beside us, and a Tim Horton's within 5 min walking distance. We offer pet friendly suites for a small charge collected upon arrival.
